anglicise.pl [--help|--man|-?] [filename ...]

Filter standard input or specified files anglicising any foreign alphabet characters and numbers.

--man   Shows help for this tool.
--help  Shows help for this tool.
-?      Shows help for this tool.

See also utf8tr.pl, math-rep.pl, utf8-ellipsis.pl, utf8-filter.pl, utf8ls-letter.sh, utf8ls-number.sh, utf8ls.pl
